{"id":232835437,"title":"[分享]英文跟讀六步驟(圖解版)","content":"「英文發音要好要跟讀，\n但到底要怎麼跟?」\n.\n大家安安:)\n這次補上跟讀圖解，供大家參考，希望有幫助:)\n.\nhttp://i.imgur.com/nofSGpD.png\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/ZSmEOHt.png\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/s1BINBv.png\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/pMHMCJq.png\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/14pwcaC.png\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/xcLRLlz.png\n [跟讀六步驟-文字版]\n1. 選擇你想要模仿的人\n假如你是男生，就盡量挑男生，比方Steve Jobs之類,這樣比較準。\n2.至Youtube下載逐字稿\nYoutube影片有個Transcript功能，可以下載講者念的稿。\n3.看逐字稿聽影片\n了解整個影片架構，以及意思是什麼。\n4.修正逐字稿\n根據講者的重輕音，把字放大縮小比方說\nI wanna(小) talk about(小) it you know(小).\n5. 聽影片聲音檔後,看稿錄音\n播放一句，比方It's William. 然後把聲音檔停住,\n看著稿想像你是那位講者，把那一句唸出來。\n6. 聽並修正\n聽自己的錄音，看跟你的講稿跟音檔有無一致。\n沒有的話就繼續修正。","excerpt":"「英文發音要好要跟讀，但到底要怎麼跟？」.，大家安安：），這次補上跟讀圖解，供大家參考，希望有幫助：），.，［跟讀六步驟-文字版］，1. 選擇你想要模仿的人，假如你是男生，就盡量挑男生，比方Steve","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"ecc6a486-c4ac-4f76-996d-7dda5dcb8518","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-06T06:44:06.446Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-06T06:44:06.446Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":22,"tags":[],"topics":["英文","圖解","英語","TOEIC","自學"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"語言","forumAlias":"language","school":"威翰英文","department":"whenglish","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":22}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/nofSGpD.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/ZSmEOHt.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/s1BINBv.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/pMHMCJq.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/14pwcaC.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/xcLRLlz.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"8f1d6970-b80f-45a5-9973-de4f7e1fe700","url":"https://i.imgur.com/nofSGpDl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/nofSGpDl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/nofSGpDl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail"